@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<div class="container py-4">
    <h2 class="h4 mb-3">Your Privacy Matters</h2>
    <p>
        Dawaya Pharmacy is committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal information.
        We only collect information necessary to provide our services, such as your name, contact details, and
        prescription information.
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Data Usage:</strong> Your information is used solely for order processing, prescription fulfillment,
            and customer support.</li>
        <li><strong>Security:</strong> We use industry-standard security measures to protect your data from unauthorized
            access.</li>
        <li><strong>No Sharing:</strong> We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties except as
            required by law or to fulfill your order.</li>
        <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> Our website uses cookies to enhance your browsing experience. You can manage your
            cookie preferences in your browser settings.</li>
        <li><strong>Account Access:</strong> You can view and update your personal information at any time by logging
            into your account.</li>
        <li><strong>Contact:</strong> If you have any questions about our privacy policy, please contact us at <a
                href="mailto:support@dawaya.com">support@dawaya.com</a>.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
        By using our website, you agree to this privacy policy. We may update this policy from time to time, and any
        changes will be posted on this page.
    </p>
</div>
